			<<link [[도망친다|Forest Wolf Cave Pair]]>><</link>>
			<br>
			<<link [[가만히 있는다 (0:30)|Forest Wolf Cave Hunt]]>><<pass 30>><</link>><<gstockholm>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<beastNEWinit 1 wolf>>
			늑대 중 한 마리가 당신에게 다가온다.
			<br><br>
			<<link [[다음|Forest Wolf Cave Molestation]]>><<set $molestationstart to 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "cabintime">>
	<<switch Time.hour>>
		<<case 6>>
			<<set _night_length to 1>>
		<<case 5>>
			<<set _night_length to 2>>
		<<case 4>>
			<<set _night_length to 3>>
		<<case 3>>
			<<set _night_length to 4>>
		<<case 2>>
			<<set _night_length to 5>>
		<<case 1>>
			<<set _night_length to 6>>
		<<case 0>>
			<<set _night_length to 7>>
		<<case 23>>
			<<set _night_length to 8>>
	<</switch>>
	<<pass _night_length hours>>
	<<if not _args[0]>> /* passing time but not sleeping */
		<<tiredness _night_length*(-12)>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "passoutforest">>
	<<if isPregnancyEnding()>>
		<<pregnancyPassout "forest">>
	<<else>>
		당신은 너무 무리했다.
		<br><br>

		<<passout>>

			<<if dangerEvent()>>
			<<if $rng gte 71 and $forest gte 21 and $settings.plantsEnabled and $settings.tentaclesEnabled and ($hallucinations gte 2 or $backgroundTraits.includes("plantlover"))>>
				<<link [[모든 것이 암흑 속으로 사라져간다...|Forest Plant Passout]]>><</link>>
			<<else>>
				<<foresthunt>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<set $foresthunt to 0>>
			<<ambulance>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<pass 1 hour>>
	<<trauma 6>><<set $stress -= 2000>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestriver">>
	당신은 물살이 빠르게 흐르는 강에 왔다.
	<<if $foresthunt gte 1>>
		당신은 이것을 추적자를 따돌리고 방해하는 데 사용할 수 있을지도 모르지만, 꽤 위험해 보인다.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[헤엄쳐 건넌다|Forest Swim]]>><<set $foresthunt to 0>><</link>><<swimmingdifficulty 1 600>>
	<br>
	<<link [[무시한다|Forest]]>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<<widget "foresttrunks">>
	마치 누군가가 지켜보는 것처럼 불안한 기분이 든다. 당신은 숲을 훑어보지만, 이상한 점은 보이지 않는다.
	<br><br>
	당신이 한 걸음을 더 내딛자, 우르릉거리는 소리가 거의 당신을 넘어뜨릴 뻔 한다. 당신의 눈앞에 있는 나무가 삐걱거리고 신음한다. 나무의 줄기가 전율한다. 가지들은 마치 보이지 않는 거인에게 끌려가듯 위로 휘어지다가, 서로 얽혀 우리를 이룬다.
	<br><br>
	딱 하는 소리와 함께 나무줄기가 당신 쪽으로 휘어지고, 가지로 이루어진 우리가 당신을 향해 달려든다.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[달린다|Forest Trunks Run]]>><</link>><<willpowerdifficulty 1 1000>>
	<br>
	<<link [[몸을 숙인다|Forest Trunks Cower]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<if $wolfgirl gte 6>>
		<<link [[울부짖는다|Forest Trunks Howl]]>><</link>><<wolfgirl>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "mushroompick">>
	<<if $forest lte 50>>
		<<set _forest_shrooms to 1>>
	<<else>>
		<<set _forest_shrooms to 2>>
	<</if>>

	당신은 <<if _forest_shrooms is 2>>썩어가는 <</if>> 나무둥치에서 먹을 수 있는 버섯 한 꾸러미를 찾았다.
	<br><br>

	<<if _forest_shrooms is 2>>
		<<if currentSkillValue('science') gte 200>>
			당신은 학교에서 그것이 <<tendingicon "wolfshroom">> 늑대 버섯이라고 불리며, 고대 전사들에게 소중히 여겨졌다고 배웠던 걸 기억해 낸다.
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>

	<<if _forest_shrooms is 1>>
		<<if $scienceshroomheart lt 5>>
			<<tendingicon "mushroom">><<link [[과학 프로젝트를 위해 가져간다 (0:02)|Forest Science Shroom]]>><<pass 2>><<set $phase to 0>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<tendingicon "mushroom">><<link [[팔 수 있을만한 버섯을 찾는다 (0:20)|Forest Mushrooms Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 1 300>>
		<br>
		<<tendingicon "mushroom">><<link [[하나 먹는다 (0:01)|Forest Mushrooms]]>><<stress 3>><<pass 1>><<tiredness -6>><</link>><<gstress>><<ltiredness>>
	<<else>>
		<<if $scienceshroomwolf lt 5>>
			<<tendingicon "wolfshroom">><<link [[과학 프로젝트를 위해 가져간다 (0:02)|Forest Science Shroom]]>><<pass 2>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if currentSkillValue('tending') lt 300 and $gwylan?.request.special is "tutorial" and $gwylanTutorialShrooms lt 3>>
			<<tendingicon "wolfshroom">><<link [[그윌란을 위해 가져간다 (0:20)|Forest Mushrooms Gwylan Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if currentSkillValue('tending') gte 300>>
			<<tendingicon "wolfshroom">><<link [[팔 수 있을만한 버섯을 찾는다 (0:20)|Forest Mushrooms2 Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 300 600>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<span class="blue">팔 수 있을만한 버섯을 채집하려면 관리 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<tendingicon "wolfshroom">><<link [[하나 먹는다 (0:01)|Forest Mushrooms2]]>><<pass 1>><<alcohol 60>><<arousal 3000>><<trauma -3>><<transform wolf 3>><</link>><<garousal>><<ltrauma>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<br>
	<<getouticon>><<link [[내버려 두는 게 좋을 것 같다|Forest]]>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forest_nest">>
	<<if !$forest_nest_intro>>
		<<set $forest_nest_intro to true>>
		<<set $forest_nest to {type: 2, fox: 3, eggs: 7}>>
		<<beastNEWinit 1 fox>>
		머리 위 나무에서 부스럭대는 소리가 들린다. <<if $anxiety gte 1>>당신은 본능적으로 가장 가까이에 있는 나무 뒤에 숨는다.<<else>>당신은 무엇인지 확인하려 조심스레 다가간다.<</if>>
		<br><br>

		당신은 우거진 나뭇잎 속 가지 다발 사이로 튀어나온 북슬거리는 주황색 꼬리를 발견한다. 여우의 보드라운 얼굴이 갑자기 당신을 올려다본다. 그의 입에는 알 한 개가 물려 있다.
		<br><br>

		그는 잠깐 주변을 둘러보더니, 시끄러운 소리를 내며 알을 깨문다. 노른자 일부가 그의 턱을 타고 흘러내린다. 그는 알을 더 가지러 둥지에 다가가,
		<<if $monster is 1>>
			여러 개를 쥐더니 나무에서 폴짝 뛰어내린다. 그는 바닥에 알을 무더기로 쌓아 놓는다.
		<<else>>
			그는 자신의 입에 알 하나를 넣더니 나무에서 폴짝 뛰어내린다. 그는 바닥에 알을 무더기로 쌓기 시작한다.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<i><span class="blue">당신도 저렇게 둥지를 오갈 수 있다면, 찾아낸 <<icon "tending/bird_egg.png">> 새알을 가져다 팔 수 있을지도 모릅니다.</span></i>
		<br><br>

		<<link [[그냥 지켜본다 (0:05)|Forest Fox Nest Watch]]>><<pass 5>><<stress -3>><</link>><<lstress>>
		<br>
		<<if $harpy gte 6>>
			<<link [[도전한다|Forest Fox Nest Challenge]]>><</link>><<harpy>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[도전한다|Forest Fox Nest Challenge]]>><</link>><<physiquedifficulty 1 $physiquemax>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<set $skulduggerydifficulty to 300>>
		<<link [[몰래 다가간다|Forest Fox Nest Sneak]]>><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
		<br>
		<<if $fox gte 6>>
			<<link [[쫓아가!|Forest Fox Nest Chase]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><<stress -6>><<transform fox 1>><</link>><<llstress>><<fox>><<note "알을 얻지 못함" "red">>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[쫓아간다|Forest Fox Nest Chase]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><<tiredness 6>><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty 1 300>><<note "알을 얻지 못함" "red">>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<set $forest_nest to {type: 0, fox: 0, bird: 0, eggs: 0}>>
		<!-- 1 = abandoned nest, 2 = active nest, 3 = fallen nest, 4 = snake nest -->
		<<rng 4>><<set $forest_nest.type to ($forest lte 50 ? Math.clamp($rng, 1, 3) : Math.clamp($rng, 2, 4))>>
		<!-- 1 = no fox, 2 = fox, 3 = player aware of fox -->
		<<if _forestNestUnsafe>>
			<<set $forest_nest.fox to 2>>
		<<else>>
			<<rng 2>><<set $forest_nest.fox to $rng>>
		<</if>>
		<<rng>>
		<<switch $forest_nest.type>>
			<<case 1>>
				<<set $forest_nest.eggs to random(1, 3)>>
				당신은 근처 나무에서 <span class="purple">버려진</span> 새 둥지를 발견했다.
			<<case 2>>
				<<set $forest_nest.eggs to ($forest gte 50 ? random(7, 14) : random(5, 10))>>
				당신은 근처 나무에서 <span class="teal">잘 관리되고 있는</span> 새 둥지를 발견했다. <<if $forest gt 50>>둥지는 썩어가는 나뭇가지에 달라붙어 있다.<</if>>
			<<case 3>>
				<<set $forest_nest.eggs to random(3, 8)>>
				당신은 땅바닥에서 <<if $forest gt 50>>진흙과<<else>>잔가지와<</if>> 나뭇잎의 큰 덩어리를 발견했다. <span class="teal">떨어진 새 둥지</span>로 보인다.
			<<case 4>>
				<<set $forest_nest.eggs to 0>>
				당신은 땅바닥에서 <<if $forest gt 50>>진흙과<<else>>잔가지와<</if>> 나뭇잎의 큰 덩어리를 발견했다. <span class="teal">떨어진 새 둥지</span>로 보인다.
				<<if currentSkillValue('tending') gte 800>>
					<<set _snakeKnown to true>>
					그러나 당신의 관리 실력에 의해, 당신은 근처의 흔적들과 땅바닥에 난 구멍을 바탕으로 <span class="red">그것이 뱀 둥지임을</span> 깨닫는다.
				<</if>>
		<</switch>>
		<br><br>
		<<if $forest_nest.fox is 2>>
			<<beastNEWinit 1 fox>>
			<<if $fox gte 6 or $cat gte 6 or $wolfgirl gte 6>>
				<<set $forest_nest.fox to 3>>
				<span class="orange">당신은 근처의 여우 냄새를 맡는다.</span> 당신은 그가
				<<if $NPCList[0].traits.includes("cowardly")>><span class="teal">겁먹었다는 것을</span> 알아챈다.
				<<elseif $NPCList[0].traits.includes("territorial")>><span class="red">영역을 지키려 한다는 것을</span> 알아챈다.
				<<elseif $NPCList[0].traits.includes("clever")>><span class="purple">영리하다는 것을</span> 알아챈다.
				<<elseif $NPCList[0].traits.includes("friendly")>><span class="green">친절하다는 것을</span> 알아챈다.
				<<elseif $NPCList[0].traits.includes("clumsy")>><span class="blue">서투르다는 것을</span> 알아챈다.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>
			<<elseif currentSkillValue('skulduggery') gte $NPCList[0].skills.security>>
				<<set $forest_nest.fox to 3>>
				<span class="blue">바스락대는 소리가 들린다.</span> 다른 무언가도 둥지를 지켜보고 있다.
				<br><br>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>

		<<if $forest_nest.type lte 2>>
			<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
				<span class="red">두 팔이 모두 묶여 있어서</span>, 당신은 나무에 오르거나 둥지를 떨어뜨릴 수 없다.
			<<else>>
				<<link [[둥지로 올라간다|Forest Nest Climb]]>><</link>><<athleticsdifficulty 0 800>>
				<br>
				<<link [[둥지를 떨어뜨린다|Forest Nest Throw]]>><<set $forest_nest.eggs -= 4>><<set $forest_nest.type to 3>><</link>><<note "Fewer eggs" "red">>
			<</if>>
			<br>
		<<elseif $forest_nest.type is 3>>
			<<link [[둥지를 수색한다|Forest Nest Search]]>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<elseif !_snakeKnown>>
			<<link [[둥지를 수색한다|Forest Nest Snake]]>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<elseif _snakeKnown and hasSexStat("deviancy", 4) and $settings.voreEnabled>>
			<<link [[당신 자신을 먹이로 제시한다|Forest Nest Snake Vore 1]]>><</link>><<deviant4>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if $forest_nest.fox is 3>>
			<<link [[숨어서 기다린다 (0:05)|Forest Nest Hide]]>><<unset $athleticsSuccess>><<set $forest_nest.eggs -= 2>><<pass 5>><</link>><<note "알을 적게 얻음" "red">>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<unset $forest_nest>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<<widget "fox_grudge">>
	<<loadNPC 0 "fox_grudge">>
	<<loadNPC 1 "fox_grudge">>
	<<loadNPC 2 "fox_grudge">>
	<<clearNPC "fox_grudge">>
	<<unset $fox_grudge>>
	여우들이 나무들 사이에서 튀어나온다. 다른 한 마리가 당신 뒤편에서 튀어나오고, 마지막으로 더욱 커다란 개체가 당신의 코앞에 나타난다. <span class="red">당신은 그가 누구인지 알아차린다.</span> 당신이 둥지에서 겁주어 쫓아냈던 바로 그 여우다.
	<<if $monster is 1>>
		"가만히 있어, 작은 여우야. 너를 갖고 놀 참이니까."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $monster is 1 or $settings.bestialityEnabled>>
		<<link [[다음|Forest Fox Revenge]]>><<set $molestationstart to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		그들은 숲을 가로질러 당신을 쫓아온다. 당신은 등 뒤에서 그들의 울음소리가 들리지 않을 때까지 달려나간다. 당신이 그것을 따돌린 건지 아니면 단지 지루해진 건지는 확실치 않다.
		<<physique 1>><<beastescape>><<gtiredness>><<tiredness 4>><<gathletics>><<athletics 2>>
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next (0:20)|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<pass 20>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestcurious">>
	<<hypnosisText "For a moment, the forest looks just a little more green.">> The foliage grows with purpose, but isn't tamed. You blink, and it looks normal again. <<hallucinogen 20>><<ghallucinogens>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[다음|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestcharms">>
	You come to a small clearing, and spot some strange shapes hanging from the tree branches above. They look like some kind of charms.
	<br><br>

	<<if $forestHunter is "Gwylan" and $foresthunt gte 1>>
		<<set $foresthunt += 1>>
		<span class="red">You feel whatever's hunting you draw closer.</span>
	<<elseif $foresthunt gte 2>>
		<<set $foresthunt -= 1>>
		<span class="blue">You feel whatever's hunting you slow down.</span>
	<<else>>
		You feel safe here, and take a moment to relax. <<stress -1>><<lstress>>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[다음|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestgwylanlure">>
	<<set $weekly.gwylanNoLure to true>>
	You hear singing <<if $forest lte 15>>close by<<else>>in the distance<</if>>.
	<br><br>

	There's something strange, yet familiar, about it.
	<br><br>

	<<set $gwylan.lureDistance to Math.clamp($forest, 15, 100)>>
	<<set $gwylan.lureWill to 0>>
	<<set $gwylan.lureSong to 1>>
	<<hypnosisText "The song worms its way into your head,">> making you feel warm.
	<<if hasSharpSenses("instincts")>>
		<span class='red'>Your <<= hasSharpSenses("instincts")>> submit and shut down immediately.</span>
	<<else>>
		<<set $gwylan.lureWill++>>
	<</if>>
	<<drugs 50>><<arousal 600>><<gdrugged>><<garousal>>
	<br><br>

	Your turn towards the source. Towards the town.
	<br><br>

	The rest of the forest blurs away as the trees part, making a clear path for you to follow. Something comforting and inviting awaits at the end.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Walk towards the singing|Forest Gwylan Lure]]>><<set $phase to "willing">><<stress -1>><<trauma -1>><<arousal 500>><<pass 5>><</link>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>><<garousal>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Resist|Forest Gwylan Lure]]>><<set $phase to "resist">><<pass 5>><</link>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestgather">>
	<<set _forest_item to random(1, 2)>>
	당신은 공터에 도착한다. 부드러운 바람이 얼굴을 간지럽히고, 작고 부드러운 식물들이 당신의 발에 눌린다.
	<<if $forest lte 20>>
		<<if _forest_item is 1>>
			키 큰 식물의 그림자 속에 백합이 잔디와 함께 자라나 있다.
		<<else>>
			잘 익은 사과가 가지에 달려 있다.
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $forest lte 50>>
		<<if _forest_item is 1>>
			야생의 빨간 장미가 곳곳이 피어 있다.
		<<else>>
			야생의 배가 나무에 자라나 있다.
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if _forest_item is 1>>
			당신은 공터 끝자락, 아주 오래된 나무의 둥치에서 난초를 발견했다.
		<<else>>
			<<if Time.isBloodMoon()>>
				<span class="red">붉은 줄무늬가 있는</span> 레몬이 작은 나무들에서 자라나 있다.
			<<else>>
				레몬이 작은 나무들에서 자라나 있다.
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<lstress>><<stress -2>>
	<br><br>
	<<if $worn.upper.exposed gte 2 and $worn.under_upper.exposed gte 1
	or $worn.upper.exposed gte 2 and $underupperwetstage gte 3
	or $upperwetstage gte 3 and $worn.under_upper.exposed gte 1
	or $upperwetstage gte 3 and $underupperwetstage gte 3>>
		<<foresticon "bush">><<link [[식물과 나뭇가지로 상의를 만든다 (0:20)|Forest Clearing]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<pass 20>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $worn.lower.exposed gte 2 and $worn.under_lower.exposed gte 1
	or $worn.lower.exposed gte 2 and $underlowerwetstage gte 3
	or $lowerwetstage gte 3 and $worn.under_lower.exposed gte 1
	or $lowerwetstage gte 3 and $underlowerwetstage gte 3>>
		<<foresticon "bush">><<link [[식물과 나뭇가지로 스커트를 만든다 (0:20)|Forest Clearing]]>><<set $phase to 2>><<pass 20>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>

	<<if $forest lte 20>>
		<<if _forest_item is 1>>
			<<if !$plants_known.includes("lily")>>
				<<if $sciencetrait gte 1>>
					<<icon "tending/lily.png">> <<link [[씨앗을 찾는다 (0:30)|Forest Lily]]>><<pass 30>><<tending 6>><<set $plants_known.push("lily")>><</link>><<gtending>>
					<br>
				<<else>>
					<span class="blue">백합 씨앗을 수확하려면 과학 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
					<br>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<<if currentSkillValue('tending') gte 100>>
				<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
					<span class="red">당신의 두 팔이 모두 묶여 있어서</span>, 백합을 꺾을 수 없다.
				<<else>>
					<<icon "tending/lily.png">> <<link [[백합을 꺾는다 (0:20)|Forest Lily Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 100 400>>
				<</if>>
				<br>
			<<else>>
				<span class="blue">팔 수 있을만한 백합을 고르려면 관리 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
				<br>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
				<span class="red">당신의 두 팔이 모두 묶여 있어서</span>, 사과를 딸 수 없다.
			<<else>>
				<<icon "tending/apple.png">> <<link [[사과를 딴다 (0:20)|Forest Apple Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 1 300>>
			<</if>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $forest lte 50>>
		<<if _forest_item is 1>>
			<<if !$plants_known.includes("red_rose")>>
				<<if $sciencetrait gte 2>>
					<<icon "tending/red_rose.png">> <<link [[씨앗을 찾는다 (0:30)|Forest Red Rose]]>><<pass 30>><<tending 6>><<set $plants_known.push("red_rose")>><<pain 6>><</link>><<gpain>><<gtending>>
					<br>
				<<else>>
					<span class="blue">붉은 장미 씨앗을 수확하려면 과학 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
					<br>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<<if currentSkillValue('tending') gte 200>>
				<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
					<span class="red">당신의 두 팔이 모두 묶여 있어서</span>, 붉은 장미를 꺾을 수 없다.
				<<else>>
					<<icon "tending/red_rose.png">> <<link [[붉은 장미를 꺾는다 (0:20)|Forest Red Rose Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 200 500>>
				<</if>>
				<br>
			<<else>>
				<span class="blue">팔 수 있을만한 장미를 고르려면 관리 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
				<br>
			<</if>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<if currentSkillValue('tending') gte 100>>
				<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
					<span class="red">당신의 두 팔이 모두 묶여 있어서</span>, 배를 딸 수 없다.
				<<else>>
					<<icon "tending/pear.png">> <<link [[배를 딴다 (0:20)|Forest Pear Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 100 400>>
				<</if>>
				<br>
			<<else>>
				<span class="blue">팔 수 있을만한 배를 고르려면 관리 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
				<br>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if _forest_item is 1>>
			<<if !$plants_known.includes("orchid")>>
				<<if $sciencetrait gte 3>>
					<<icon "tending/orchid.png">> <<link [[씨앗을 찾는다 (0:30)|Forest Orchid]]>><<pass 30>><<tending 6>><<set $plants_known.push("orchid")>><</link>><<gtending>>
					<br>
				<<else>>
					<span class="blue">난초 씨앗을 수확하려면 과학 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
					<br>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<<if currentSkillValue('tending') gte 300>>
				<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
					<span class="red">당신의 두 팔이 모두 묶여 있어서</span>, 난초를 꺾을 수 없다.
				<<else>>
					<<icon "tending/orchid.png">> <<link [[난초를 꺾는다 (0:20)|Forest Orchid Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 300 600>>
				<</if>>
				<br>
			<<else>>
				<span class="blue">팔 수 있을만한 난을 고르려면 관리 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
				<br>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if currentSkillValue('tending') gte 200>>
				<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
					<span class="red">당신의 두 팔이 모두 묶여 있어서</span>, 레몬을 딸 수 없다.
				<<else>>
					<<if Time.isBloodMoon()>>
						<<icon "tending/blood_lemon.gif">> <<link [[레몬을 딴다 (0:20)|Forest Blood Lemon Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 200 500>>
					<<else>>
						<<icon "tending/lemon.png">> <<link [[레몬을 딴다 (0:20)|Forest Lemon Pick]]>><<pass 20>><</link>><<tendingdifficulty 200 500>>
					<</if>>
				<</if>>
				<br>
			<<else>>
				<span class="blue">팔 수 있을만한 레몬을 고르려면 관리 스킬이 더 높아야 합니다.</span>
				<br>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>

	<<foresticon>><<link [[계속 걸어간다|Forest]]>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanitem">>
	<<print either("트로피","야구공","야구 방망이","스노우 글로브","마법의 8번 당구공","탁구채","체스 세트","돼지저금통","머그컵","쿠키 상자","프라이팬","효자손","연필통","도시락 상자","용암 램프","손전등","뻐꾸기 시계","루빅스 큐브","지구본","물총","사전","손거울","싸구려 카메라","조개껍데기가 꽉찬 집락 비닐백","작은 발판사다리","어디 쓰이는지 모를 골동품")>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "slimePunishmentForest">>
	슬라임이 당신이 반항한 것에 대해 벌을 주며 당신은 강한 고통을 느낀다.
	<<corruption -1>><<pain 8>><<stress 6>><<trauma 6>><<def 1>><<lcorruption>><<ggpain>><<ggtrauma>><<ggstress>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestRescueSetup">>
	/* 	Eden is available if they're a love interest 50% of the time or if they've never rescued the player before
		Gwylan is available based on how deep in the forest the player is, with conditions changing how deep they can rescue from
		If Gwylan is Nobody, they're available as Nobody regardless of where in the forest the player is */
	<<set $canRescue to []>>
	<<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
	<<if isGwylanAbsent() is "nobody">>
		<<set $canRescue.push("Nobody")>>
	<<elseif $forest lte gwylanForestRescueRange() and (!C.npc.Gwylan.init or C.npc.Gwylan.state is "active") and !_gwylanStatus?.includes("wounded") and !$npc.includes("Gwylan") and ["shop","garden","sleep"].includes(gwylanSchedule())>>
		<<set $canRescue.push("Gwylan")>>
	<</if>>
	<<if (isLoveInterest("Eden") and (random(1, 2) is 2 or $eden_rescue isnot 1)) and !$npc.includes("Eden")>>
		<<if !$npc.includes("Black Wolf")>>
			<<set $canRescue.push("Eden")>>
		<<elseif $npc.includes("Black Wolf") and $canRescue.includes("Gwylan")>>
			/* Eden only rescues against the Black Wolf if Gwylan also can, for balance purposes */
			<<set $canRescue.push("Eden")>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $rescue to $canRescue.length gte 1 ? 1 : 0>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestRescueCheck">>
	<<if $alarm is 1>>
		<<if $rescue is 1>>
			<<if $canRescue.length gt 1>>
				<<set $_noText to true>>
			<<elseif $canRescue.includes("Gwylan") and ["Eden","Black Wolf","bear"].includes(_args[0]) and !(isGwylanAbsent() is "nobody")>>
				<<if $gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_sex")>>
					<span class="forest-green">근처 나무에서 바스락거리는 소리가 들린다.</span>
				<<else>>
					<<gwylanRescueStats false _args[0]>><<set $rescue to 0>>
					<<if _args[0] is "Eden">>
						<<if C.npc.Eden.name_known>>
							<<set $_assailant to "Eden">>
						<<else>>
							<<set $_assailant to "the <<= C.npc.Eden.title>>">>
						<</if>>
					<<elseif _args[0] is "Black Wolf">>
						<<set $_assailant to "the Black Wolf">>
					<<else>> <!-- Currently only applies to bears -->
						<<set $_assailant to "the <<beasttype>>">>
					<</if>>
					당신은 고함소리에 놀란 <<if $forest_shop_intro is 1 or $gwylan_rescue is 1>>그윌란이<<else>>칙칙한 갈색머리의 남자가<</if>> 나무줄기를 헤치고 뛰어 나오는 것을 본다. 그는 그  $_assailant를 한 번 보고는, <span class="red">돌아서서 도망친다.</span>
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				<<set $_noText to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if $gwylan_rescue is 1>>
				<span class="red">그윌란은 당신을 도우러 오지 않는다<<if _args[0] isnot "Eden" and $syndromeeden is 1>>. 에덴은 이 구역에 오지 않을 것이다<</if>>.</span>
			<<else>>
				<span class="red">당신이 마을에서 너무 멀리 떨어진 곳에 있어서 누구도 당신의 소리를 들을 수 없다<<if _args[0] isnot "hunter" and $syndromeeden is 1>>. 에덴은 이 구역에 오지 않을 것이다<</if>>.</span>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<set $_noText to true>>
	<</if>>
<<if $alarm is 1 and $rescue is 0>>
		<<set $alarm to 0>>
	<</if>>
	<<if !$_noText>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestRescue">>
	<<set $rescued++>>
	<<if $NPCList[0].fullDescription is "Black Wolf">>
		<<set $_type to "Black Wolf">>
	<<elseif $NPCList[0].fullDescription is "Eden">>
		<<set $_type to "Eden">>
	<<elseif $monster is 1>>
		<<silently>><<beastSimple>><</silently>>
		<<set $_type to _text_output>>
	<<else>>
		<<set $_type to $NPCList[0].type>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $_lands to _args.includes("river") ? "splashes" : "lands">>
	<<set $_forest to _args.includes("river") ? "water" : "forest">>
	<<set $_backsOffAnd to _args.includes("snow") ? "kicks up fistfuls of snow as <<bhe>>" : "backs off in fear and">>
	<<if $canRescue.includesAll("Eden","Gwylan")>> <!-- co-op rescue -->
		<<gwylanRescueStats true $_type "Eden">><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

		<<if $_type is "plant">>
			You hear a gun fire close by, and a bullet pierces the ground at the <<person1>><<persons>> feet. At the same time, a ?gwylanItem crashes into the <<persons>> face. <<He>> yelps and retracts <<his>> vines, burrowing into the earth.
		<<elseif $_type is "human">>
			<<if $enemynomax is 1>>
				You hear a gun fire close by, and a bullet pierces the ground at the <<person1>><<persons>> feet. At the same time, a ?gwylanItem crashes into the <<persons>> face.
				<<if _args.includes("cutter")>>
					<<He>> staggers back, but seems more worried about the gunshot. "The maniac," <<he>> whispers.
				<</if>>
				<<He>> backs off in fear and flees into the forest.
			<<else>>
				You hear a gun fire close by, and a bullet pierces the ground at the <<= $enemynomax is 2 ? "pair" : "group">>'s feet. At the same time, a ?gwylanItem crashes into the <<person1>><<persons>> face. They back off in fear and flee into the forest.
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $_type is "bear">>
			<<set $_close to true>><<hallucinogen 120>>
			The <<beasttype>> growls, but is hit in the face by a flying pouch. Powder erupts from it, and you're caught in the cloud. It smells funny.
			<br><br>

			<<bHe>> growls again, swiping <<bhis>> nose, before freezing in fear. <<bHis>> eyes are locked on something behind you. You look over your shoulder.
			<br><br>

			<<if $edenCagedEscape or edenFreedomStatus() gte 2 or !$gwylanRescue.eden>>
				<span @class="_gwylanFirstRescue is 'bear'?'red':''">A massive, inhuman monster stalks towards you. It's twice your size, with two long necks holding up a pointed, faceless head.</span>
				<<if _gwylanFirstRescue is "bear">>
					<span class="red">Even the trees around it seem to stretch taller.</span> <<stress 12>><<trauma 6>><<ggstress>><<gtrauma>>
				<<else>>
					You've seen this before. <span class="forest-green">It's Gwylan.</span>
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				<<if $monster is 1>>
					"Too big," the <<beasttype>> whispers, backing up. <<bHe>>
				<<else>>
					The <<beasttype>> pounds <<bhis>> paws against the ground nervously, before <<bhe>>
				<</if>>
				$_backsOffAnd flees into the forest.
				<br><br>

				"Hey, relax. You're alright."
				<<if _gwylanFirstRescue is "bear">>
					<span class="red">The giant steps towards you, its necks unnaturally pulling its pointy head into its torso. It produces what looks like a cloth and presses it to your nose. Everything...</span>
					<br><br>

					...clears up. You blink. The trees no longer stand quite so tall. The creature is gone too. In its place is a mousy <<nnpc_gendery "Gwylan">> wearing a witch hat and an amused smile. <span class="green">It's Gwylan.</span>
				<<else>>
					Gwylan steps towards you, what you now recognize as <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> arms pulling <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> hat back down. <<He>> dabs something from a small bottle into a cloth and presses it to your nose. Everything returns to normal size.
				<</if>>
				"Breathe. It's always a trip, I know."
				<br><br>

				<<if _gwylanFirstRescue is "bear">>
					<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> bends down to pick up the now-empty pouch, showing it to you. "Surprised? Some spores have halluinogenic properties. That one warps your perception, making everything look larger than it really is. And making yourself look bigger is the best way of scaring off bears." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> takes off <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> hat and holds it over <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> head for emphasis, before putting it back on.
					<br><br>
				<</if>>

				A gunshot rings out, interrupting <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">>. It pierces the ground near the still-retreating bear. You turn and see a figure emerge from the bushes.
				<<if $edenCagedEscape or edenFreedomStatus() gte 2>>
					<span class="red">It's Eden</span>. <<nnpc_He "Eden">> marches over to you, and doesn't look happy to see you.
				<<else>>
					It's Eden.
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				Two shapes emerge from the bushes. <span @class="_gwylanFirstRescue is 'bear'?'red':''">One is a massive, inhuman monster twice your size with two long necks holding up a pointed, faceless head. The other is a mouthless creature with its spine jutting out at an angle to its neck.</span>
				<<if _gwylanFirstRescue is "bear">>
					<span class="red">Even the trees around them seem to stretch taller.</span> <<stress 12>><<trauma 6>><<ggstress>><<gtrauma>>
				<<else>>
					You've seen this before. <span class="forest-green">It's Gwylan,</span> but there's somebody else, too.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				The second creature's spine dislodges, pointing at the bear and letting out a deafening pop. Something pierces the ground by its feet.
				<br><br>

				<<if $monster is 1>>
					"Too big," the <<beasttype>> whispers, backing up. <<bHe>>
				<<else>>
					The <<beasttype>> pounds <<bhis>> paws against the ground nervously, before <<bhe>>
				<</if>>
				$_backsOffAnd flees into the forest.
				<br><br>

				"Hey, relax. You're alright."
				<<if _gwylanFirstRescue is "bear">>
					<span class="red">The giant steps towards you, its necks unnaturally pulling its pointy head into its torso. It produces what looks like a cloth and presses it to your nose. Everything...</span>
					<br><br>

					...clears up. You blink. The trees no longer stand quite so tall. The creatures are gone too. In their places are a mousy <<nnpc_gendery "Gwylan">> wearing a witch hat and an amused smile, and a muscular <<nnpc_gender "Eden">> with a rifle in <<nnpc_his "Eden">> arms. <span class="green">It's Gwylan and Eden.</span>
				<<else>>
					Gwylan steps towards you, what you now recognize as <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> arms pulling <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> hat back down. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> dabs something from a small bottle into a cloth and presses it to your nose. Everything returns to normal size.
				<</if>>
				"Breathe. It's always a trip, I know."
				<<if _gwylanFirstRescue is "bear">>
					<br><br>

					<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> bends down to pick up the now-empty pouch, showing it to you. "Surprised? Some spores have halluinogenic properties. That one warps your perception, making everything look larger than it really is. And making yourself look bigger is the best way of scaring off bears." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> takes off <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> hat and holds it over <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> head for emphasis, before putting it back on.
					<br><br>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $_type is "Black Wolf">>
			/* exit case, does not continue to rest of widget */
			You hear a sound like glass breaking nearby. A green light briefly blinds you. The Black Wolf backs away from you, becoming sluggish. You hear singing. Your head feels fuzzy. <<hallucinogen 120>><<gghallucinogens>>
			<br><br>

			<span class="forest-green">Gwylan</span> emerges from the treeline as the light slowly fades from the Black Wolf's eyes. <<bHe>> backs away and growls, still half-lucid. "Shhhh." Gwylan kneels down, producing a small vial full of blue powder and smiling at you.
			"You should go, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>. I'll handle..." <<nnpc_His "Gwylan">> eyes widen.
			<br><br>

			The black wolf sniffs the air, then drops low, <span class="red">just as a bullet whizzes by.</span> The impact showers the wolf with splinters of bark, and the sound snaps <<bhim>> out of <<bhis>> shallow trance.
			<<bHe>> looks between you, Gwylan, and the culprit emerging from the treeline. <span class="green">It's Eden.</span>
			<br><br>

			Eden quickly shoulders <<nnpc_his "Eden">> rifle again, taking aim. The Black Wolf darts off into the forest. The shot impacts another tree. "Almost."
			<br><br>
			Eden takes aim at Gwylan next, rage painted on <<nnpc_his "Eden">> face. "Get away from <<phim>>. Now."
			<br><br>

			Gwylan doesn't move. "And leave <<phim>> with you?" <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> stares down the barrel of Eden's rifle.
			<br><br>
			
			<<link [[Run|Forest Trio Confrontation]]>><<set $phase to "run">><<stress 12>><</link>><<ggstress>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Try to calm them down|Forest Trio Confrontation]]>><<stress 12>><<set $phase to "stand">><</link>><<ggstress>>
			<br>
			<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 5>>
				<<link [[Step in front of the gun|Forest Trio Confrontation]]>><<set $phase to "front">><<stress 50>><<trauma 25>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 5>><</link>><<gggstress>><<gggtrauma>><<ggyearning>>
			<</if>>
			<br>
			<<exit>>
		<<else>>
			<<set $_gwylanThrow to "capsule">>
			A small capsule lands nearby, and starts to let out a series of sparks and loud pops. At the same time, you hear gunfire close by, and a bullet $_lands near the <<beasttype>>. Overwhelmed, <<bhe>> $_backsOffAnd flees into the $_forest.
			<<if $combatTrain.total_length isnot undefined>>
				The <<= $combatTrain.total_length is 1 ? "others follow" : "other follows">> after <<bhim>>.
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<clotheson>>
		<<endcombat>>

		<<npc Eden 1>><<person1>>
		<<if ($edenCagedEscape or edenFreedomStatus() gte 2) and $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
			<<npc Gwylan 2>><<person1>>
			<<if !$_close>>
				<<gwylanDesc "cap">> emerges from the treeline and rushes to your side.
				<<if $gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_beast")>>
					"Are you alright, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>?"
				<<else>>
					"Are you alright, dear?"
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				You hear more rustling. <span class="red">Eden</span> emerges next and marches towards you. <<He>> doesn't look happy to see you.
			<</if>>

			<<if $gwylanRescue.eden gte 4>>
				<<He>> grabs Gwylan by the arm and pulls <<person2>><<him>> aside, but <<person1>><<his>> gaze remains fixed on you.
				<br>
