				I have a shop right by the outskirts of the forest," <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> says. "You can't miss it. I sell—" <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> pauses. "My grand<<father>> sells—" another pause. "I sell clothes and knick-knacks there. <span class="blue">Things you won't find in normal shops.</span> Even I don't know what I have in stock!" <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> sounds proud. Eden snorts.
