			You hear a sound like glass breaking nearby. A green light briefly blinds you. The Black Wolf becomes sluggish. You hear singing. Your head feels fuzzy. <<hallucinogen 120>><<gghallucinogens>>
			<br><br>

			<span class="forest-green">Gwylan</span> emerges from the treeline as the light slowly fades from the Black Wolf's eyes. <<bHe>> backs away and growls, still half-lucid. "Shhhh." Gwylan kneels down, producing a small vial full of blue powder and smiling at you.
			<<if _gwylanStatus?.includes("reunion")>>
