			<<if $hunterintro isnot 1 or !$syndromeeden>>
				/* Eden backs down due to not being attached enough to PC, continue to normal rescue text */
				<<He>> sighs, <span class="green">and lowers it.</span> "Fine. This isn't over. There are gaps in your vision, <<witch>>." <<He>> slings <<his>> rifle over <<his>> shoulder and walks into the forest.
				<br><br>

				Gwylan watches <<him>> leave, and rushes to your side once <<hes>> gone. "Are you alright? That brute didn't hurt you, did <<he>>?"
			<<else>>
				/* exit case, does not continue to rest of widget */
				"<<pShes>> going home. Even if I have to drag <<phim>> there."
				<br><br>

				<<person2>>Gwylan continues approaching.
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners") and $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1 or $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
					"That's right, <<pshe>> is going home. But it's not the home you think. <<gwylanCommand "Come along, <<pcpetname 'Gwylan'>>.">>" Gwylan holds out <<his>> hand to you.
					<br><br>

					"Touch <<phim>> and I'll blow your fucking hand off," <<person1>><<he>> yells. <span class="blue">You hear a dull click.</span> Eden looks down at <<his>> rifle with annoyance.
					<br><br>

					Gwylan's hand remains reaching out to you. "You'll miss," <<person2>><<he>> says flatly. "Just like you always do."
					<br><br>

					<<link [[Take Gwylan's hand|Forest Gwylan Eden Rescue]]>><<set $phase to "Gwylan">><<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>><<npcincr Eden love -10>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<ggyearning>><<llllove "Eden">>
					<br>
					<<link [[Stay with Eden|Forest Gwylan Eden Rescue]]>><<sub 1>><<set $phase to "Eden">><<npcincr Gwylan dom -10>><<npcincr Eden dom 3>><</link>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>><<lllyearning>><<ggdom "Eden">>
					<br>
				<<else>>
					"That cabin isn't a home, Eden. No matter how much you play pretend." Gwylan lifts <<his>> hat, looking Eden directly in the eyes now. "Have you ever once asked <<phim>> what <<pshe>> wants?"
					<br><br>

					Eden winces. "Shut it. I know what's best for <<phim>>." <<person1>><<His>> grip trembles. <span class="blue">You hear a dull click.</span> Eden looks down at <<his>> rifle with annoyance.
					<br><br>

					"You don't even know what's best for yourself," Gwylan says, shaking <<person2>><<his>> head. <<He>> turns to you. "Do you want me to take you back to the shop?"
					<br><br>

					<<link [[Nod|Forest Gwylan Eden Confrontation]]>><<set $phase to "Gwylan">><<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>><<npcincr Eden love -10>><</link>><<ggyearning>><<llllove "Eden">>
					<br>
					<<link [[Say you want to go with Eden|Forest Gwylan Eden Confrontation]]>><<sub 1>><<set $phase to "Eden">><<npcincr Gwylan dom -10>><<npcincr Eden dom 3>><</link>><<lllyearning>><<ggdom "Eden">>
					<br>
				<</if>>
				<<exit>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>> /* beast */
			<<if $gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_beast") and $rng gte 51>>
				The <<beasttype>> <<beast_growls_text $_type>>, but it quiets down as you hear something else. Singing.
				<<if $_type.includes("boar")>>
					<<bHe>> grunts, looking around, before slowly bowing <<bhis>> head.
					<<if $monster is 1>>
						"Can't think..."
					<</if>>
				<<elseif $_type.includes("lizard")>>
					<<bHe>> looks around, alarmed, but slowly calms.
				<<else>>
					<<bHe>> yelps and looks around, alarmed, but <<bhis>> posture relaxes.
					<<if $monster is 1>>
						"Human song! Where... human..."
					<</if>>
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				<<gwylanDesc "cap">> slowly emerges from the treeline, singing a gentle melody. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> approaches and kneels down, petting the <<beasttype>>. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> leans in and whispers. "Go home."
				<br><br>

				<<if $_type.includes("boar")>>
					<<bHe>> huffs a few times, but starts to walk away.
				<<elseif $_type.includes("lizard")>>
					<<bHe>> lets out a low hiss, and vanishes beneath the water.
				<<else>>
					<<bHe>> scurries away, <<bhis>> tail between <<bhis>> legs.
				<</if>>
				<<if $combatTrain.total_length isnot undefined>>
					The <<= $combatTrain.total_length is 1 ? "others follow" : "other follows">> <<bhim>>.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				<<gwylanDesc>> lets out a sigh.
			<<else>>
				The <<beasttype>> <<beast_growls_text $_type>>, but is silenced as a small capsule lands next to you. The capsule starts to spark and pop loudly.
				<<if $_type.includes("boar")>>
					<<bHe>> grunts, looking around.
					<<if $monster is 1>>
						"Tricks and traps. I hate."
					<</if>>
				<<elseif $_type.includes("lizard")>>
					<<bHe>> looks around, alarmed.
				<<else>>
					<<bHe>> yelps and looks around, alarmed.
					<<if $monster is 1>>
						"Human attack! Where human?!"
					<</if>>
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				Another one lands nearby, and starts to pop. Overwhelmed by the noise,
				<<if $_type.includes("boar")>>
					<<bhe>> runs away.
				<<elseif $_type.includes("lizard")>>
					<<bhe>> dives back into the churning water.
				<<else>>
					<<bhe>> scurries away, <<bhis>> tail between <<bhis>> legs.
				<</if>>
				<<if $combatTrain.total_length isnot undefined>>
					The <<= $combatTrain.total_length is 1 ? "others follow" : "other follows">> <<bhim>>.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				<<gwylanDesc "cap">> emerges from the treeline.
			<</if>>
			"Are you alright? I swear they get more aggressive every day," <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> mutters.
		<</if>>

		<<if _args.includesAny("river","snow")>>
			<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> grasps your arm and pulls you out of the <<= _args.includes("river") ? "water" : "snow">>.
		<</if>>
		/* Prevents towelup when the player has clothes */
		<<silently>><<clotheson>><</silently>>
		<<if $exposed gte 1>>
			<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> offers you some old towels to <<if _args.includesAny("river","snow")>>dry yourself and <</if>>cover up.<<dry_towel>>
		<</if>>
		<<if $pain gte 50>>
			<<if $gwylanSeen?.includes("partners")>>
				<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> kisses you on the cheek before tending to some of your bruises.
			<<else>>
				<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> spends some time soothing your bruises.
			<</if>>
			<<pain -15>>
		<</if>>

		<<if _gwylanFirstRescue is "bear">>
			<br><br>

			<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> bends down to pick up the now-empty pouch, showing it to you. "Surprised? Some spores have halluinogenic properties. That one warps your perception, making everything look larger than it really is. And making yourself look bigger is the best way of scaring off bears." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> takes off <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> hat and holds it over <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> head for emphasis, before putting it back on.
		<</if>>

		<<if $_combatEnded>>
			<<endevent>>
			<br><br>
		<<else>>
			<<clotheson>>
			<<endcombat>>
		<</if>>
		<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>

		<<if _gwylanStatus?.includes("reunion")>>
			<<He>> pulls you into a tight hug.
			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
				"Now, where have you been? Do you have any idea how worried I was?" <<if _gwylanTF.revealed>><<His>> tail beats on the ground.<</if>>
			<<else>>
				"I'm glad I found you. I haven't seen you in ages, I thought you were gone for good. What happened to you?"
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<gwylanReunion>>
			<br><br>

			<<if _gwylanStatus?.includes("badEndReady")>>
				<<He>> doesn't let go. "Please, just let me hold you for a little while. I really though this would be the end. I thought I'd be alone again."
				<br><br>

				You feel the slightest pinprick in your arm. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
				<br><br>

				<span class="purple">The forest starts to shift and distort.</span> Gwylan's face remains in perfect clarity at the centre of your vision. <<He>> smiles sweetly, holding up a pink rose. Its stem drips red. <<hallucinogen 160>><<ggghallucinogens>>
				<br><br>

				The ground attacks you from below, but Gwylan guides you down slowly. "Shhh... just... a little longer."
				<br><br>

				<<hypnosisText "<<His>> sweet voice silences your thoughts, and you're no longer where you once were.">> <<His>> voice fades away with the rest of the forest.
				<br><br>

				<<if _gwylanStatus?.includes("aurigaScarConfront")>>
					<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Nowhere Passout]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
				<<else>>
					<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Taken Start]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
				<</if>>
				<br>
				<<exit>>
			<<else>>
				<<He>> withdraws.
			<</if>>
		<<elseif !_gwylanStatus?.includes("met")>>
			<<set $daily.gwylan.firstMet to true>>
			<<He>> looks about your age, with mousy hair and freckles. "I'm older than I look," <<he>> says, as if reading your mind. "<span class="green">I'm Gwylan.</span> Nice to meet you."
			<br><br>

			"I have a shop right by the outskirts of the forest," <<he>> says. "You can't miss it. I sell—" <<He>> pauses. "My grand<<father>> sells—" Another pause. "I sell clothes and knick-knacks there. <span class="blue">Things you won't find in normal shops.</span> Even I don't know what I have in stock!" <<He>> sounds proud.
			<br><br>
		<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed>>
			<<gwylanRescueApology>>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<if $gwylanRescue.eden gte 1 and !$gwylanRescue.failed and $_type isnot "Eden">>
			<<He>> looks around for a moment, as if waiting for something. "Strange," <<he>> says to <<himself>>. "I thought the <<nnpc_title "Eden">> would be here, too."
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<gwylanRescueNotice>>

		<<if _gwylanStatus?.includes("reunion") or Time.dayState is "night">>
			<<He>> looks back into the treeline one last time. "Would you like to walk back to the shop with me? It would be safer together."
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Yes|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<set $phase2 to "combatEnded">><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
			<br>
			<<link [[No|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 2>><<set $phase2 to "combatEnded">><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<if $_gwylanThrow is "item">>
				<<He>> gathers <<his>> items, then walks off in the direction of <<his>> shop.
			<<else>>
				<<He>> walks off in the direction of the shop.
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<if _args.includes("slime")>>
				<<slimePunishmentForest>>
				<br><br>
			<</if>>

			<<link [[Next|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $canRescue.includes("Nobody")>>
		Nobody comes to rescue you.
		<br><br>

		<<if $_type is "plant">>
			Nobody stands between you and the <<person>>.
			<br><br>

			The <<person>> flinches back at nobody. <<He>> looks at you, face ashen, and withdraws <<his>> vines.
			<br><br>

			"I'm sorry," <<he>> whispers, before turning and running through the forest. "I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I didn't mean to! I didn't mean to! I..." <<His>> voice becomes inaudible. <<tearful>> you gather yourself.
		<<elseif $_type is "human">>
			<<if $enemynomax gt 1>>
				Nobody stands between you and the <<group>>.
			<<else>>
				Nobody stands between you and the <<person>>.
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			Nobody saves you.
			<br><br>

			<<if $enemynomax gt 1>>
				The <<group>> are gone.
			<<else>>
				The <<person>> is gone.
			<</if>>
			<<tearful>> you gather yourself.
		<<elseif $_type is "Eden">>
			<<set $_edenName to C.npc.Eden.name_known ? "Eden" : "the <<nnpc_title 'Eden'>>">>
			Nobody stands between you and <<= $_edenName>>.
			<br><br>

			<<= $_edenName.toUpperFirst()>> scowls, but <<his>> face turns pale.
			<br><br>

			Nobody gets shot at.
			<br><br>

			Nobody seems to mind.
			<br><br>

			Nobody approaches.
			<br><br>

			<<= $_edenName.toUpperFirst()>> flees.
			<<tearful>> you gather yourself.
		<<elseif $_type is "Black Wolf">>
			The Black Wolf suddenly withdraws from you, staring off into the treeline.
			<br><br>

			<<bHis>> tail puffs up, and <<bhe>> growls. <<bHe>> looks to you, then back to the trees.
			<br><br>

			<<bHe>> flees.
			<br><br>

			You look around, worried about what could have possibly frightened <<bhim>>. You quickly understand.
			<br><br>

			Nobody is here.
			<br><br>

			<<tearful>> you gather yourself.
		<<else>> /* beast */
			<<if $combatTrain.total_length isnot undefined>>
				Nobody stands between you and the <<beastsplural>>.
			<<else>>
				Nobody stands between you and the <<beasttype>>.
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			Nobody saves you.
			<br><br>

			<<if $combatTrain.total_length isnot undefined>>
				The <<beastsplural>> are gone.
			<<else>>
				The <<beasttype>> is gone.
			<</if>>
			<<tearful>> you gather yourself.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<clotheson>><<set $gwylanRescue.failed to "">>
		<<endcombat>>

		<<if _args.includes("slime")>>
			You feel the slime in your ear's displeasure at your defiance.
			<br><br>

			Nobody whispers in your ear. You hear nothing, but <span class="lblue">the slime falls silent</span>.
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		You're alone.
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Forest]]>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<elseif $canRescue.includes("Eden")>>
		You hear a gun fire close by, and a bullet $_lands
		<<if $_type is "plant">>
			<<set $_hikers to "hikers">>
			at the <<persons>> feet. "Fuck," <<he>> hisses. "It's the <<nnpc_title "Eden">>. Fuck. Fuck shit fuck. Um." <<He>> grabs your face and gives you a syrupy kiss on each cheek, before pulling away from you. "See ya! I'm out!"
			<<if $edenCagedEscape>>
				The <<person>> retracts <<his>> vines and retreats into the forest.
			<</if>>
			<<bodyliquid "face" "nectar">>
		<<elseif $_type is "human">>
			at the <<person1>><<persons>> feet.
			<<if _args.includes("cutter")>>
				"The maniac," <<he>> whispers.
			<</if>>
			<<if $enemynomax gt 1>>
				<<set $_hikers to "hikers">>
				The <<= $enemynomax is 2 ? "pair" : "group">> back off in fear and flee into the forest.
			<<else>>
				<<set $_hikers to "bastard">>
				<<He>> backs off in fear and flees into the forest.
			<</if>>
		<<else>> /* beast */
			<<set $_hikers to $_type>>
			near the <<beasttype>>. <<bHe>> $_backsOffAnd flees into the
			<<if $combatTrain.total_length isnot undefined>>
				$_forest, the <<= $combatTrain.total_length is 1 ? "other" : "others">> following close behind.
			<<else>>
				$_forest.
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<if $edenCagedEscape>>
			<<clotheson>>
			<<endcombat>>

			<<npc Eden>><<person1>>
			Before you have a chance to recollect, you feel a hand on your shoulder. You're spun around, and come face-to-face with Eden, <<his>> eyes full of rage.
			<br><br>

			"You've got some nerve," <<he>> growls. "Abandoning me, acting like a fucking brat, then expecting me to save your helpless ass."
			<br><br>

			<<He>> grabs your wrist tight and begins marching you into the woods. "Come on. You're overdue for your punishment."
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Resist|Forest Eden Rage]]>><<set $phase to 0>><<def 1>><<npcincr Eden dom -1>><</link>><<physiquedifficulty 2000 18000>><<ldom>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Submit (0:30)|Forest Eden Rage]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<pass 30>><<sub 1>><<npcincr Eden dom 1>><</link>><<gdom>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<if $_type is "plant">>
				The <<person>> retracts <<his>> vines and retreats into the forest right as Eden emerges. <<nnpc_He "Eden">>
			<<else>>
				Eden emerges and
			<</if>>
			helps you collect yourself. "Damn <<= ["hikers","bastard"].includes($_hikers) ? $_hikers : "<<beastSimple $_hikers true>>">>," <<nnpc_he "Eden">> mutters. "Are you okay?"
			<br><br>

			<<clotheson>>
			<<endcombat>>
			<<if $gwylanRescue?.eden gte 1>>
				<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar">>
					Eden glances at your collar, frowning in thought. Whatever <<nnpc_hes "Eden">> thinking, <<nnpc_he "Eden">> doesn't voice it.
				<<else>>
					Eden glances around for a moment. "We must be in too deep for that shopkeep," <<nnpc_he "Eden">> says.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>
			<</if>>

			<<if $eden_rescue isnot 1>>
				<<set $eden_rescue to 1>>
				Eden pats you on the shoulder. "I was able to hear you because I happened to be in the area," <<nnpc_he "Eden">> says. "<span class="gold">I might not always be around, but I should be able to save you anywhere in the forest.</span> Give me a shout if you're in trouble."
				<br><br>
			<</if>>

			<<forestCabinReturnLinks>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<span class="red">Invalid rescue in $passage: <<print $canRescue>>!</span> Please report this.
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Forest]]>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanRescueApology">>
	<<if $gwylanRescue.failed is "WraithFight">>
		Gwylan quickly hugs you as you walk in. "I'm so sorry.
	<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "Wraith">>
		<<set $_noFollowUp to true>>
		<<if _args.includes("shop") and !_args.includes("intro")>>
			<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> looks you over with concern.
		<<else>>
			"Hey," Gwylan says as you walk in. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> looks concerned.
		<</if>>
		"Are you feeling okay? You look a little pale, and I thought I heard you screaming the other night..."
	<<else>>
		<<if _args.includes("shop")>>
			<<if _args.includes("intro")>>
				<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> rubs the back of <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> neck. "By the way, sorry
			<<else>>
				"Hey," Gwylan says as you walk in. "Sorry
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> can't meet your gaze. "Sorry
		<</if>>
	<</if>>

	<<if $_noFollowUp>>
		/* Nothing */
	<<else>>
		<<if $gwylanRescue.failed is "WraithFight">>
			I'm glad you were able to get away from the Ivory one." <<He>> steps away and rubs <<his>> neck. "It sure knows how to hold a grudge."
		<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "EdenAttack">>
			for not being able to save you from <<= $gwylanRescue.eden gte 1 ? "Eden" : "the <<nnpc_title 'Eden'>>">>. I wasn't expecting <<nnpc_him "Eden">> to be such a brute."
		<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "EdenShop">>
			for not being able to keep <<= $gwylanRescue.eden gte 1 ? "Eden" : "the <<nnpc_title 'Eden'>>">> from taking you. I had a plan... but I suppose <<nnpc_he "Eden">> made <<nnpc_his "Eden">> move too quickly for it to take effect."
		<<else>>
			for not saving you before, but I can't contest
			<<if $gwylanRescue.failed is "Eden" and $gwylanRescue.eden gte 1>>
				Eden. Nobody's bulletproof."
			<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "Eden">>
				the <<nnpc_title "Eden">>. <<nnpc_Hes "Eden">> the second scariest thing in the forest."
			<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "Black Wolf">>
				the alpha. I don't want the entire pack breaking my door down."
			<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "bear">>
				a bear. We are but tasty, squishy morsels compared to them."
			<<else>>
				...uh... the $gwylanRescue.failed? Wait, what were you fighting again? Who?" Gwylan rubs the back of <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> neck. "<span class="red">Bweh. I think there's a bug here.</span>"
				<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> shakes <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> head. "<<gwylanCommand "Report this to PurityGuy">> when you have the time, okay, dear?"
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>

	<<if _args.includes("Robin")>>
		/* Todo: Gwylan, Robin gets different reactions when closer to Gwylan? */
		Robin blinks, but doesn't question it.
	<</if>>

	<<set $gwylanRescue.failed to "">>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanRescueApologyEden">>
	<<if $gwylanRescue.failed is "WraithFight">>
		Gwylan hugs you. "I'm so sorry that I couldn't free you from the Ivory one." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> rubs <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> neck. "It sure knows how to hold a grudge."
		<br><br>

		Eden looks bemused. "The Ivory one? Save your ghost stories."
	<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "Wraith">>
		Gwylan eyes you with concern. "I'm glad we found you this time. I thought I heard you scream the other night, but I couldn't find you."
		<br><br>

		Eden eyes you with suspicion.
	<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "Eden" or $gwylanRescue.failed is "EdenAttack" or $gwylanRescue.failed is "EdenShop">>
		Gwylan frowns for a moment.
		<<if $gwylanRescue.failed is "EdenAttack">>
			"No hard feelings, but you best keep your hands to yourself this time. Play nice."
		<<else>>
			"I better see you playing nice this time."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		Eden sighs, crossing <<nnpc_his "Eden">> arms. "<<pShe>> needs to learn to obey me."
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("petplay") and $gwylanRescue.eden gte 4>>
			<br>
			Gwylan giggles. "<<pShe>> obeys me just fine. Maybe you need lessons."
			<br>
			"Don't push your luck, <<witch>>."
			<br>
			"Oh? Would you prefer a collar, then?"
			<br>
			"I have plenty."
		<<else>>
			Gwylan doesn't seem happy with that reply, but doesn't push it.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

	<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "Black Wolf">>
		<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> can't meet your gaze. "Sorry for not saving you before, but I can't contest the alpha. I don't want the entire pack breaking my door down."
		<br><br>

		"You were attacked by the alpha? The black one?" Eden growls. "If that thing lays a single mangy paw on you, I'll hunt myself a nice black rug."
		<br><br>

		<<if $gwylanRescue.eden gte 4>>
			"Yes, surely you'll best it next time," Gwylan says with a laugh. "Just like the last nine times."
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $gwylanRescue.failed is "bear">>
		<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> can't meet your gaze. "Sorry for not saving you before, but I couldn't contest a bear alone. We are but tasty, squishy morsels compared to them."
		<br><br>

		Eden nods.
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
	<<set $gwylanRescue.failed to "">>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestCabinReturnLinks">>
	<<link [[Go back to the cabin (0:30)|Forest Cabin Return]]>><<pass 30>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Say goodbye|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</widget>>

<!-- Argument one is minimum -->
<<widget "tending_bird_eggs">>
	<<if _args[0] gt 0>>
		<<set $_min to _args[0]>>
		<<if _args[1]>>
			<<set $_max to _args[0]>>
		<<else>>
			<<if $forest_nest and $forest_nest.type>>
				<<switch $forest_nest.type>>
					<<case 1>><<set $_max to (_args[0] + 2)>>
					<<case 2>><<set $_max to (_args[0] + 7)>>
					<<case 3>><<set $_max to (_args[0] + 4)>>
				<</switch>>
			<<else>>
				<<set $_max to (_args[0] + 4)>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<<wearProp "bird egg">>
		<span class="green"><<tending_pick bird_egg $_min $_max>></span>
	<<else>>
		<span class="red">There's no intact eggs left.</span>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestBullyLeaves">>
	<br><br>
	그들이 떠난 후, 당신은 탈출할 방법을 찾는다. 밧줄을 타고 가지로 올라갈 수도 있지만, 그 높이는 상당하다. 도움을 요청하는 것 외에 다른 방법은 없어 보이지만, 주의를 끄는 것은 상황을 더 악화시킬 수 있다.
	<br><br>
	<<link [[기어오른다|Forest Bully Climb]]>><</link>><<athleticsdifficulty 0 1055>>
	<br>
	<<link [[도움을 요청한다|Forest Bully Help]]>><</link>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "forestsnow">>
	The snow here has not been cleared in a long time. It's reaching up to your knees, and becomes deeper the further you continue.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Turn back (0:15)|Forest]]>><<pass 15>><<if $foresthunt gte 1>><<set $foresthunt += 1>><</if>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Keep going|Forest Snow]]>><</link>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanRescueNotice">>
	<<if $gwylan_rescue isnot 1 or $gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_sex") and ($worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and !$gwylanRescue.seen.includes("collarScream") or $fox gte 6 and !$gwylanRescue.seen.includes("foxScream"))>>
		<<set _gwylanRescueNotice to true>>
		<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> starts to walk off, but stops and turns around. "By the way," <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> says.
		<<if $gwylan_rescue isnot 1>>
			<<set $gwylan_rescue to 1>>
			"I was able to hear you because you were close enough to my shop.
			<<if $gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_sex")>>
				<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar">>
					<<set $gwylanRescue.seen.pushUnique("collarScream")>>
					While you're wearing this..." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> brushes <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> fingers against your collar affectionately. "<span class="forest-green">I'll be able to hear you throughout the entire forest.</span> Otherwise...
				<</if>>
				<<if $fox gte 6>>
					<<set $gwylanRescue.seen.pushUnique("foxScream")>>
					I'll be able to hear you up to the border of the deepest parts of the forest, but that's only as long as you have that <span class="orange">foxiness</span> to you. If you lose it...
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<span class="gold">If you go any further than the start of the lake, I won't be able to hear you.</span> Keep it in mind."
		<<elseif !$gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_sex")>>
			<!-- Do nothing -->
		<<elseif $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $fox gte 6 and !$gwylanRescue.seen.includesAny("collarScream","foxScream")>>
			<<set $gwylanRescue.seen.pushUnique("collarScream","foxScream")>>
			<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> brushes <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> fingers against your collar affectionately. "As long as you're wearing this, <span class="forest-green">I'll be able to hear you throughout the entire forest.</span> And even if you're not, as long as you have that <span class="orange">foxiness</span> to you that you do now, I'll be able to hear you up to the border of the deepest parts of the forest. Keep it in mind."
		<<elseif $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and !$gwylanRescue.seen.includes("collarScream")>>
			<<set $gwylanRescue.seen.pushUnique("collarScream")>>
			<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> brushes <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> fingers against your collar affectionately. "As long as you're wearing this, <span class="forest-green">I'll be able to hear you throughout the entire forest.</span> Keep it in mind."
		<<elseif $fox gte 6 and !$gwylanRescue.seen.includes("foxScream")>>
			<<set $gwylanRescue.seen.pushUnique("foxScream")>>
			"As long as you have that <span class="orange">foxiness</span> to you that you do now, I'll be able to hear you up to the border of the deepest parts of the forest. Keep it in mind."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>
